    <frbrLevel>Expression</frbrLevel>
    <semanticLevel>PreIconographical</semanticLevel>
    <rdfs:comment>The canonical visual medium of the named template as derived from the representative image via CLIP. Property of the Expression-level MemeConcept.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">The visual medium of the canonical meme image&#13;
(Photograph, Drawing, Cartoon, Illustration, Painting, etc.). Pre-iconographical&#13;
classification at the Manifestation level, assigned via CLIP-based scoring.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing"/>
  </rdf:Description>
